Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: China's spoilt brats
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wx37
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 2 Jan 1983
China admits its 'one child' rule has led to a generation of - mainly male - spoilt brats. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less